        <h2>Assembly</h2>
        <hr>
        <p>This step in the computer building process is when every component comes together inside the case. It may
            seem like a daunting task, but the act of assembling your computer is comparable to assembling Legos. All
            parts have designated slots in the case or on the motherboard, and each part comes with detailed manuals if
            you ever need extra information on that specific part.</p>
