            <p class="caption">A prepared workspace for a computer build [8]</p>
        </div>
        <p>Before continuing with the actual assembly, it's important to prepare your work area with everything you'll
            need to build the computer:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>All parts of the computer unboxed and nearby. Keep delicate components like the CPU or GPU in their wrappers
                after taking them out of the box.</li>
            <li>Open computer case (both side panels taken off)</li>
            <li>Phillips head screwdriver</li>
            <li>Light source (e.g. flashlight)</li>
            <li>Zip ties or twist ties</li>
            <li>Thermal paste</li>
        </ul>
